{"tid":305014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民陣因天雨關係取消政總集會","createTime":"2017-07-01T10:59:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-01T18:20:06.000Z","uid":41404,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2ee5044e821459312564a1611597cd1cb42235b7","tid":305014,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T10:59:46.000Z","msg":"民陣下午發起七一遊行，隊伍由維園草坪出發，經過不足2小時就抵達終點政府總部，但因天雨關係，原訂在政總外舉行的集會宣布取消。<br />\n<br />\n今年遊行的主題是「一國兩制呃足廿年，民主自治重奪香港」。<br />\n<br />\n有參與人士表示要繼續爭取民主，亦有市民要求內地釋放病重的諾貝爾和平獎得主劉曉波。"},{"pid":"8382cd928ff962ecaf648af15e7e6d18a755b805","tid":305014,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T11:02:15.000Z","msg":"鳩做<br />\n廢事俾人話五毛左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b323b8cf3e27471f4030e750c5ae026f31468fa","tid":305014,"uid":57797,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T11:03:43.000Z","msg":"收撚完捐款唔撚走咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c10f657b8e852c862644ae8a3940056a0efbe18","tid":305014,"uid":53903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T11:05:07.000Z","msg":"應該係少人到唔想柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64952f2aff23d84f0eaed5d415f7152ea34a8bf7","tid":305014,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T11:09:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該係少人到唔想柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該都多人過琴晚既"},{"pid":"a4c4a236e010323a5d2430a7a4f26179ad0a1482","tid":305014,"uid":45232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T11:12:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>應該係少人到唔想柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該都多人過琴晚既</blockquote><br />\n今年無報人數？唔見有相關新聞"},{"pid":"d39606e753eaf5024753f11f02ef1643b1076e6e","tid":305014,"uid":34572,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T11:13:39.000Z","msg":"又話無懼雨怎麼打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69a6beea591167401436b1b2bae965785fcfc215","tid":305014,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T11:19:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4cd291221d763c3ab4083cf2a11579d5c1f354a7","tid":305014,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T11:22:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該係少人到唔想柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊會有人信佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0d027566847cd78afc342c7401e27c2812cf37a","tid":305014,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T11:23:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>應該係少人到唔想柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該都多人過琴晚既</blockquote><br />\n今年無報人數？唔見有相關新聞</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n民陣宣布有逾<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">六萬人</span></span>參與七一遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=949336&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D949336%26csid%3D261_341&d=29H9Uu4z%2BZjOFlWrOCwtgf755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=6dbd2722\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=949336&amp;csid=261_341</a><br />\n<br />\n民陣發起七一遊行，要求落實普選，及內地釋放患末期肝癌的異見人士劉曉波。民陣晚上宣布有超過六萬人參與。遊行隊伍下午三時半前，由維園中央草坪出發，龍頭到下午五時半前抵達終點政府總部，由於天雨關係，民陣取消集會，原定的嘉賓對談活動改為網上直播，參與市民到達終點後陸續散去，龍尾亦快將抵達政府總部。<br />\n<br />\n遊行期間，有團體代表約三十人手持五星紅旗，在灣仔警察總部對開，向遊行人士叫「愛國愛港、支持警察、反對港獨」等口號。另外，多名戴口罩並手持印有「香港獨立」橫額，及龍獅旗的人士，在灣仔鵝頸橋走入民陣的遊行隊伍，去到警察總部外時停下，高叫「香港獨立」等口號。監警會亦派員視察七一遊行情況。"},{"pid":"bc6e7eef6cb881ef9573252c50fac9953e96cf13","tid":305014,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T11:23:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>應該係少人到唔想柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該都多人過琴晚既</blockquote><br />\n今年無報人數？唔見有相關新聞</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nApple Daily just reported the turn-out number.  Around 60k."},{"pid":"e84327fb1a42da9dd93b6cde3ef3dd2aa818984d","tid":305014,"uid":80563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T11:24:24.000Z","msg":"錢已籌夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb5265baf301134e2144ab7c4dfa6ea50b17b5db","tid":305014,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T11:24:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.881903.com/News_Images/NewsBoss/resize/20170701_20170701-171602.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FNews_Images%2FNewsBoss%2Fresize%2F20170701_20170701-171602.jpg&h=4e13f74d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n高舉香港獨立人士加入遊行隊伍 (商台新聞)"},{"pid":"07f441440b4490e198f6ff7eaf2c59c6015b0f55","tid":305014,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T11:25:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>錢已籌夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實人數唔係最重要<br />\n<br />\n最重要籌款夠"},{"pid":"f40b7659b67159360cc6397365b5746f7c63d066","tid":305014,"uid":110019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T11:37:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>錢已籌夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實人數唔係最重要